Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,800)\pos(210,66.5)\fs31\bord0\fsp2}星之海原
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏又遇上雷雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來就很難找到信號微弱的求救信號了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎兒 他們兩個一定會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這麼大的雨 搜救會很困難的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小班 別說些多餘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是連救援的人也遇到危險的話 只會徒增麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我冷靜 騎士團已經前往救援了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙也是有優點的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很讓人意外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就交給我們 所有人都回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果騎士團已經出動了 那就沒有我們能做的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服從教官的命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也一樣 聽懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在這裡等他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真不走運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨這麼大 救援隊也來不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這雨要是能在天黑前停下來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 還有卡路兒跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3-5和3-6區域已搜索完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的區域由於暴風雨而延後搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緊急降落到水上的話 就要在海上過夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能堅持住就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎兒 你真的打算一直留在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 我們也在這裡陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男生也是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在這裡等嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們兩個一定能平安歸來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從那時起就一直在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:05:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天晚上的事我記得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「風之革命」之後 某天我們家裡突然來了個陌生男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你們新的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他從今天開始就住在我們家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他名字叫卡路兒·阿巴斯 是你們的乾弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 真棒 是弟弟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口渴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫諾兒 16歲 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我姐姐就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫曼紐爾 12歲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個可愛的弟弟真高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移開視線了 真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 太可愛了 他在害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:05:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎你也來自我介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喏 快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是艾黎兒 今年九歲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 艾黎兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼不開心的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他多大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 還沒問他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路兒你幾歲了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九歲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和艾黎同歲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡爾 你的生日呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6月6日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你的哥哥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是6月7日出生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你們才總是妹妹弟弟的爭個不停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他為什麼到艾黎兒家去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是親戚之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的父母過世了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父親不忍心 就把他帶回我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路兒也很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是卡路一開始什麼都不說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡爾 這叫拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好吃 嚐嚐看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 肚子不餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道你出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是連話都不回 真是太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我才是你的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比你乖多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算沒精神也能吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人跟我講話 我也會回答
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 艾黎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路是因為突然間被帶到了一個不熟悉的家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才這麼緊張的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 是緊張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 這也算哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是嬰兒至少也會知道回應嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面對突然到來的外人 我一時難以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 該睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐們還要準備明天的早飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母后…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的媽媽在我剛出世的時候就過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也十分理解沒有母親時的寂寞心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和卡路雖然不是親兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在一起長大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路和克莉亞一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是兩個人單獨相處 卡路他不會覺得不知所措嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不能告訴大家 卡路真正的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 我們必須得把便當給爸爸送去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 艾黎兒 你也要去看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廣場上正在上演「風之革命」的戲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜大人 請您原諒我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您一定原諒我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今才知求饒 真是難看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝葛列國里歐 皇后瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們窮奢極欲的時候 民眾卻生活在水深火熱之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你毀掉了國家 該死的魔女 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 達米安 你也住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向母后道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母后？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路兒…就是王子 卡爾·拉·伊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橡皮艇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,積水了 得把橡皮艇翻過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:11:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行嗎 我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一會兒 就會乾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克莉亞 用這個釣魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣魚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用再三道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我有生以來第一次釣魚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我釣過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是和艾黎 諾兒 曼紐爾一起釣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 是姐姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎兒有兩個姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著夕陽 就會回想起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次飛上藍天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸是飛機維修員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 我們去給他送便當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過半路上 我跟鎮上的壞孩子打了一架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 爸爸 午飯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經傍晚了 你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班頭 麻煩 試飛一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要飛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一直都能飛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐到後面去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起飛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當前高度 300米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高度 500米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高度 800米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1200
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1800
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡高的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛 高度2000
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊就是亞歷山大城
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好廣闊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 是海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道海的對岸 都有些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想親眼見識下 「天空的盡頭」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「天空的盡頭」…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就替我去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要飛起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一刻 我下定決心 一定要成為飛行員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 跟你聊這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚 不上鉤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚現釣現吃是很美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎處理之後 會做成各種料理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的能耐只在料理上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴巴惡毒 動不動就打人 羅圈腿 睡相差
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有的事 艾黎是個很出色的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有這回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 艾黎很在乎卡路兒你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！你是這麼覺得的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎總是生我氣 發我牢騷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是為了卡路兒你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎現在一定也很擔心卡路兒你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去之後 要好好道歉 好好感謝她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才謝謝你 衝著想去救他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你是個會為同伴著想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太抬舉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們倆 天亮就會回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 什麼都沒釣到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克莉亞 要小睡一會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該會睡不著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就繼續聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次說說克莉亞你的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克莉亞為什麼會想成為飛行員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人不反對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是跟媽媽分開生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟弟弟也分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是路易斯提督讓孤獨的我登上了伊斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路易斯提督？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 原來我們兩個很像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「風之革命」之後 我也失去了親生父母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤單一人的時候被現在的父親收養了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我和艾黎兒也沒有血緣關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前一直在亞歷山大生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候都不曾打理自己的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿巴斯家的人教我了許多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是稍微睡一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在「風之革命」中失去雙親 生活於亞歷山大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候都不曾打理自己的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴雷特洛斯前皇太子 卡爾·拉·伊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許偷偷混進伊斯拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後準備向妮娜·維恩特復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克莉亞 是騎士團的飛行編隊 我們得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝天謝地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 果然兩人都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎 抱歉 讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大家這麼操心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你又笨又馬虎又不正緊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害得克莉亞也跟你一起遭罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害大家在這裡留宿 快道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快和大家道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害大家這麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 艾黎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才對您去上飛行學校抱有異議
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是打倒罪惡 扶助正義的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼喚風 駕馭風的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是妮娜·維恩特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是伊格納修
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙上次只穿內褲 這次又只穿泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.27,0:23:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個胡鬧的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能這樣囂張也只是現在了 內褲…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.76,0:23:39.77,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs32}第五話 呼喚風的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:36.55,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}逃げる場所さえなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:42.81,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}窓から見上げてるだけで精一杯の
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:49.80,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}あの日の僕にも君がくれたその言葉の意味すら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:54.50,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}まだ分かりはずもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.71,0:01:02.04,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}絶望という名の雲の端へ飛べた世界に住む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:09.92,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕らにいまとっても強い風が吹いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:15.31,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}一緒にどこまでも飛べる気がしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:20.52,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}初めて見つけた自由握り締めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:28.37,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}まだ何も知らずに浸れた僕の幼好きた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:35.71,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}青い青い空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:42.81,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}無處可逃 僅僅透過窗台仰望天空經已竭盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:49.80,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那天給予我的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:54.50,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}其真意依舊琢磨不透
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.71,0:01:02.04,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}飛越名為絕望的雲端 棲身於希望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:09.92,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}逆著狂烈的疾風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:15.31,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}堅信著定能一同飛向天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:20.52,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}將初次獲得的自由緊握手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:28.37,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}沉浸在年少時情有獨鍾的未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:35.71,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那片蔚藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:18.63,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}愛の言葉じゃ そこに出せない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:25.20,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}届かない想いが 吹き荒れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.31,0:22:31.15,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}その身体には 鎧は重すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:37.99,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}未完成の心の 鍵を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:47.21,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}戦うわけなど あるとするのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:50.29,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}1つだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:54.64,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}震えている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.98,0:23:01.97,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}君を放っておけないのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:14.07,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}必ずそこまで 迎えに行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:27.69,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}その体温は僕と 風が知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:18.63,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}在那兒 愛的話語 無法說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:25.20,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}無法傳達的思念 如舞風媻娑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.31,0:22:31.15,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}對這個身體而言 負擔太重太多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:37.99,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}尋找那不成熟的內心的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:47.21,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}戰鬥的理由 如果有的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:50.29,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那麼就只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:54.64,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}心在顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.98,0:23:01.97,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}無法棄你於不顧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:14.07,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}一定會去那兒迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:27.69,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}你的體溫 唯有風兒和我知曉
